<div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; font-family: 'Apple SD Gothic Neo', 'Malgun Gothic', sans-serif; color: #333;">
  <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e53e3e 0%, #dd6b20 100%); padding: 32px; text-align: center;">
    <h1 style="color: #fff; margin: 0; font-size: 24px;">EnterLab</h1>
    <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); margin: 8px 0 0;">예약 취소 안내</p>
  </div>

  <div style="padding: 32px; background: #fff;">
    <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
      안녕하세요, <strong><%= @reservation.name %></strong>님!<br>
      예약이 취소되었습니다.
    </p>

    <div style="background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
      <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
        <tr>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0; color: #666; width: 120px;">취소된 일시</td>
          <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: 600;"><%= @datetime %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
      다시 예약을 원하시면 언제든 방문해 주세요.<br>
      문의사항: <strong><%= @contact %></strong>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 16px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #999;">
    &copy; EnterLab. All rights reserved.
  </div>
</div>
